    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## I.TRACK — Site Event Collector\nPublic beacon endpoint for reece-tracker.js (main site, GHL pages, Weakest Point LP).\n\n**Webhook** POST /webhook/reece-track → responds 200 immediately (onReceived).\n**HTTP Request** forwards the full webhook item (body + x-forwarded-for) to LP-MCP `/n8n/site/collect`, which whitelists fields, folds the client IP into raw.ip, and inserts into public.site_events (025 schema) via the service-role client. I.STITCH then stitches identify rows every 5 min.\n\nFire-and-forget: neverError + continueOnError so a bad payload never breaks the beacon.",
